00:02:05,870 --> 00:02:07,790
seperti Guru Jiang.

11
00:02:08,070 --> 00:02:09,190
Tapi, perasaanku terhadap Guru Jiang

12
00:02:09,190 --> 00:02:11,550
lebih seperti rasa hormat
junior pada seniornya.

13
00:02:09,660 --> 00:02:13,889
