125
00:07:34,910 --> 00:07:35,990
Tentu saja.

126
00:07:35,990 --> 00:07:38,030
Uang itu yang paling penting.

127
00:07:38,470 --> 00:07:39,870
Royalti penjualan "The Book of Luohe"
yang kuberikan padamu

128
00:07:39,870 --> 00:07:43,150
