130
00:07:47,190 --> 00:07:49,950
masih banyak barang yang mau kubeli.

131
00:07:49,950 --> 00:07:53,030
Misalnya baju baru.

132
00:07:53,030 --> 00:07:54,380
Bantal baru.

133
00:07:54,380 --> 00:07:56,510
Sofa baru.

134
00:07:56,510 --> 00:07:59,070
Kalau begitu lebih baik
aku membelikan rumah untukmu.

135
00:08:03,390 --> 00:08:05,180
Cukup. Cukup. Jangan minum lagi.

136
00:08:05,180 --> 00:08:05,990
Dengan kebiasaan minum begini,

137
00:08:05,990 --> 00:08:07,820
lain kali jangan minum di luar.

138
00:08:08,110 --> 00:08:09,230
Tidak mau.

139
00:08:09,230 --> 00:08:10,510
Kamu bukan pacarku.

140
00:08:10,510 --> 00:08:11,550
Jangan sok mengaturku.

141
00:08:11,550 --> 00:08:14,190
Kuberitahu, ya. Aku kuat minum.

